{
  "stem": "5313.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I had about a year, you know, really fun to do what they did to me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To be ordered, you know, to be people watching it, you know, not to get out of line.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Germans, you know, we would have any more over there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they had camp from civilian, from the English soldiers-- civilians, you know, who worked there, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was my responsibility, to keep it in gear.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, not to get any riots or so on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And also to help, you know, people, you know, what they needed help, you know, to get in the camp what they needed.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When-- you talk about--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I went to Hungary, my mother and father stayed in Romania.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They put him into ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They was putting it together and they putting in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Since I recall, at that time, I was in Hungary, you know, with forged papers, I tried to go to see them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I went from Hungary to Romania with-- I had Hungarian name, forged paper that I'm not a Jew and with a train, you know.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I can imagine my feeling, you know, how I felt at that time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I wanted to see what I can do for my parents.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But they were surrounded already into the ghetto and I had no chance to get into that ghetto.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I met some people that I know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they said, you better disappear.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They're getting-- every Jews they're putting together and putting into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So the following day, I had no choice that I just went back to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I know that they took them also to the Germans camps, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother died in a concentration camp, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
